      "title": "Lanka IOC to suspend fuel delivery for Friday (8) and Saturday (9)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Lanka IOC has decide to suspend the delivery fuel to filling stations today (8) and tomorrow (9).",
        "The decision was taken taking into account the number of protests planned for the two days.",
        "Lanka IOC will continue to deliver fuel to CPC and industries.",
